<span>'''胡椒酸'''（{{lang-en|Piperic Acid}}）是一种常通过[[胡椒碱|胡椒碱]]的水解制得的化学物（该反应的另一样产品是一分子[[哌啶|哌啶]]）</span><ref>{{Cite book|url = http://books.google.com/?id=iyzlMSPp-EMC&pg=PA327|page = 327|isbn = 978-0-470-74167-2|author = Paul M. Dewick.|year = 2009|publisher = A John Wiley & Sons|location = Chichester|title = Medicinal natural products : a biosynthetic approach}}</ref> 。胡椒碱则天然存在于[[胡椒|胡椒]]果实中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://chestofbooks.com/health/aromatherapy/The-Volatile-Oils-Vol1/Heliotropin.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-09-05 |archive-date=2010-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212121317/http://chestofbooks.com/health/aromatherapy/The-Volatile-Oils-Vol1/Heliotropin.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>http://www.erowid.org/archive/rhodium/chemistry/3base/piperonal.pepper/degradation.piperine/index.html</ref> 胡椒酸是生物化学中合成一些有机物（如[[胡椒醛|胡椒醛]]）以及制取其他香料或熏香产品以及药物的有用中间产物。 

